captions.text: Shit old pepole say
Come here, my darling!
I made you a little something to eat.
You are all skin and bones!
Does your mom even feed you?
Jesus, you have a tattoo!

When I used to swore,
my dad spanked me hard.

The mold doesn't matter,
you can just cut it off.
Have you got a boyfriend already?
Have you got your amant already?

People sit on this
and you put your dirty shoes on it!
Get out of that lawn, you punks!
I will cal SNB on you!
Good old communists.

- What? - What? - I can't hear you!
- What did you say?
Cut your hair, Milan, you look ridiculous.
Milk is discounted!
Where are my teeth?
In my days...

- When I was young...
- I was already married at your age
and I was pregnant with your mom.
Did I take my pills today?
Just for sure.
Are you hungry?
Janicka...
oh, Janicka is that other one...
Lenicka!

Are you going on your vacation
to Yugoslavia again?

Can you send those emails
on Sunday too?
I'm coming!
I'm not that stupid to fall for something.

You are a gas expert?
Well come on in then.
You big goon!
If only I can live to see it.
I won't be here too long.

You will not believe,
who died this time.

You are going to give me
your seat, won't you?
Sit, sit, I'm getting off on the next stop.
I'm not going on that computer,
I could get some virus.

Here I have this modern
blouse after my mom,
do you want it?
Next, please.
I was here first!
Oh, those todays kids.
Oh, now I can see it.

- What did I want to do here?
- Where am I?
We have won a million!
Don't you know, where are my glasses at?

And so I tell him:
"In the handout it says 21,90

and you tell me it costs 22,50,"
so I tell him, I don't want it.
Jesus!

You are leaving?
Take some pickles on the road.
Take some cherries, too.
And these homemade eggs.
Bye.
